548
00:46:46,303 --> 00:46:48,305
<i>Oh Ga-in mora longe.</i>

549
00:46:50,706 --> 00:46:52,659
<i>Tem um salão de beleza
em Gyeonggi.</i>

550
00:46:55,498 --> 00:46:57,111
